  "name": "Dueling Mastery",
  "type": "feat",
  "img": "icons/skills/melee/weapons-crossed-swords-yellow-teal.webp",
  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>Requirement: Melee, One weapon in one hand, No Weapon in other hand.</p><p> Your mastery of fighting with a single melee weapon is peerless.</p><p> You make one weapon feel like many.</p><p> You gain the following benefits: </p><p>• The first time each turn you score a hit with a melee weapon attack; you increase your damage by +1 weapon damage die.</p><p> • When a creature hits you with a melee attack, you can use your reaction to make an immediate melee weapon attack against the triggering creature.</p><p></p>",
